meta.name: Add Document
meta.description: Add a single document to MeiliSearch. Accepts a JSON object representing the document and adds it to the index

meta.name: Add Documents
meta.description: Add a list of documents to MeiliSearch index.

meta.name: Delete Document
meta.description: Delete a document from a Meilisearch index.

meta.name: Get Document
meta.description: Retrieve a document from a Meilisearch index using the given Document ID.

meta.name: Full Text Search
meta.description: Performs a full text search on a Meilisearch index

meta.name: Hybrid Search
meta.description: Performs a hybrid search combining full-text and attribute-based filtering, returning a JSON object or an array of them. For more details on using vector search in MeiliSearch, visit the [official documentation](https://www.meilisearch.com/docs/learn/experimental/vector_search#using-vector-search).

meta.name: Update Document
meta.description: Update a single document in MeiliSearch. Accepts a JSON object representing the document and updates it.

meta.name: Update Documents
meta.description: Update multiple documents in MeiliSearch by sending an array of JSON objects.

meta.name: Update Synonyms
meta.description: Update the synonyms for any index in your MeiliSearch instance
